OL,3,C'It's Armageddon': Pub landlady says
OL,4,Crising costs are threatening livelihood
OL,6,FA landlady at a pub in Hampshire says
OL,7,Fshe is facing "Armageddon" because
OL,8,Frising costs and a drop in footfall
OL,9,Fare putting her livelihood at risk.
OL,11,FAnnmarie McCarthy has been running The
OL,12,FSwan Inn in Barton Stacey for several
OL,13,Fyears but says it has become a
OL,14,F"nightmare" following the pandemic.
OL,16,FThe former coaching house has stood in
OL,17,Fthe village for more than three
OL,18,Fcenturies.
