OL,3,C'It's Armageddon': Pub landlady says
OL,4,Crising costs are threatening livelihood
OL,6,FHowever, like many pubs across the
OL,7,Fcountry, its future is uncertain with
OL,8,FMs McCarthy no longer able to open
OL,9,Feveryday because of rising bills and a
OL,10,Fdrop in trade.
OL,12,FShe's been told her costs will rise by
OL,13,F#12,000 this year alone which is money
OL,14,Fshe doesn't have.
OL,16,F"It's Armageddon to me, but I
OL,17,Funderstand I really understand, that
OL,18,Fpeople have got a finite amount of
OL,19,Fmoney", she explained.
