OL,3,C'It's Armageddon': Pub landlady says
OL,4,Crising costs are threatening livelihood
OL,6,F"So have I. They don't seem to think
OL,7,Fthat because you're a pub - it is a
OL,8,Fbusiness - but I haven't got any money
OL,9,Feither.
OL,11,F"I can't see it getting any better.
OL,12,FCome April it is just going to be an
OL,13,Fabsolute nightmare."
OL,15,FAcross the country more than 400 pubs
OL,16,Fclosed last year with more expected to
OL,17,Ffold in 2025.
