OL,3,C'It's Armageddon': Pub landlady says
OL,4,Crising costs are threatening livelihood
OL,6,FAt the Frog and Frigate in Southampton
OL,7,Fowners have cut down the opening hours
OL,8,Fto just two evenings a week to keep
OL,9,Fthe business going.
OL,11,FLandlord, Derek Gardener, said:
OL,12,F"There's no way that we could operate
OL,13,F7 days a week, there is just no way.
OL,15,F"If we tried to open for 7 days a
OL,16,Fweek, the utility prices, the wages,
OL,17,Fit would break us.
