OL,3,C'It's Armageddon': Pub landlady says
OL,4,Crising costs are threatening livelihood
OL,6,F"We just wouldn't be able to do it.
OL,7,FThe fact that we only do open on those
OL,8,Ftwo nights a week - it's targeted -
OL,9,Fand people know where we are."
OL,11,FThe government insists it is taking
OL,12,Faction to support pubs and the wider
OL,13,Fhospitality industry.
OL,15,FA new permanent lower business rate
OL,16,Ffor pubs is set to be introduced next
OL,17,Fyear which the government says will
OL,18,Fprovide support to more than 250,000
OL,19,Fvenues.
